function info($str) { echo "INFO: $str\n"; }
function warn($str) { echo "WARNING: $str\n"; }
function err($str) { die("FATAL ERROR: $str\n"); }

@set_time_limit(0);

@header('Content-Type: text/plain');

chdir(__DIR__);
if (trim(@file_get_contents('oidplus_version.txt')) !== 'Revision 359') {
	err('This update can only be applied to OIDplus version 2.0.0.359!');
}

if (version_compare(PHP_VERSION, '7.0.0') < 0) {
	err('You need PHP Version 7.0 to update to this version');
}

}

if (is_file('dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps') && (sha1_file('dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps') != 'd01f03011179b463ed84dc5a1ce9f0ed5fc96efe')) {
	warn('File was created by someone else. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps');
	$tmp = pathinfo('dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps');
	$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
	warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
	if (!@copy('dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps', $backup_name)) {
		warn('Creation of backup failed');
	}
}
writefile_3();
if (!is_file('dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps')) {
	warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps');

	warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps');
} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps', 0755)) {
	warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps');
}

if (is_file('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps') && (sha1_file('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps') != 'ac877d4f579f76f13d2ed500470209e7e881a2a3')) {
	warn('File was created by someone else. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps');
	$tmp = pathinfo('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps');
	$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
	warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
	if (!@copy('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps', $backup_name)) {
		warn('Creation of backup failed');
	}
}
writefile_4();
if (!is_file('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps')) {
	warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps');
} else if (sha1_file('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps') != 'ac877d4f579f76f13d2ed500470209e7e881a2a3') {
	warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps');
} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps', 0755)) {
	warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps');
}

	$tmp = pathinfo('res/Tools/uuid_generator_big.png');
	$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('res/Tools/uuid_generator_big.png')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');

}

if (!is_file('TODO')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: TODO');
	writefile_43();
	if (!is_file('TODO')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): TODO');
	} else if (sha1_file('TODO') != '685b9542b2734219aa0cb0a333b6f08caae6afff') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): TODO');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('TODO', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of TODO');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('TODO') !== '685b9542b2734219aa0cb0a333b6f08caae6afff') {
		if (@sha1_file('TODO') !== '3e78788f595ce69960b853acdeb7be7e0a7ccbdb') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: TODO');
			$tmp = pathinfo('TODO');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('TODO')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('TODO', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_43();
		if (@sha1_file('TODO') !== '685b9542b2734219aa0cb0a333b6f08caae6afff') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): TODO');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	writefile_48();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') != '9edc413934c8fcccc81dbc63b3a8baa8beabbddb') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') !== '9edc413934c8fcccc81dbc63b3a8baa8beabbddb') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') !== '6a13490b8a0246dbe649b0ecdcdaccf0d4c2ce2c') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_48();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') !== '9edc413934c8fcccc81dbc63b3a8baa8beabbddb') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
		}
	}
}

			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusAuthUtils.class.php');

			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusAuthUtils.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_49();

			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusAuthUtils.class.php');

		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php') !== '999a0daf6a64020137c731629090079d0ff9712d') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_50();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php') !== 'df1296990732f87f50cbd9da604808748bc6038a') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
	writefile_55();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php') != 'bb6395b3810b3009b2bd2a0d9e4508fbad3d780e') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php') !== 'bb6395b3810b3009b2bd2a0d9e4508fbad3d780e') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php') !== '2f6037837b5ef721d0f8da88c23824f5248da880') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_55();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php') !== 'bb6395b3810b3009b2bd2a0d9e4508fbad3d780e') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
		}
	}
}

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php') != '45a93b5c40e0a595c02d809740c3f3d0df822735') {

	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php');
	}

	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php') !== '45a93b5c40e0a595c02d809740c3f3d0df822735') {

			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_56();

if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusSessionHandler.class.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplusSessionHandler.class.php');
	writefile_59();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusSessionHandler.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusSessionHandler.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusSessionHandler.class.php') != '4e593a19615d91fecea1e4f944f9f7cfded94b3d') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusSessionHandler.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusSessionHandler.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusSessionHandler.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusSessionHandler.class.php') !== '4e593a19615d91fecea1e4f944f9f7cfded94b3d') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusSessionHandler.class.php') !== '6ce64feb5afdaf95a6e47b030e08f84b99ab5713') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusSessionHandler.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusSessionHandler.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusSessionHandler.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusSessionHandler.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_59();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusSessionHandler.class.php') !== '4e593a19615d91fecea1e4f944f9f7cfded94b3d') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusSessionHandler.class.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/classes/VtsBrowserDownload.class.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/VtsBrowserDownload.class.php');
	writefile_60();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/VtsBrowserDownload.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/VtsBrowserDownload.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/VtsBrowserDownload.class.php') != 'd40f1144839238e983ec043dc5210a772df7fdbf') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/VtsBrowserDownload.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/VtsBrowserDownload.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/VtsBrowserDownload.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/VtsBrowserDownload.class.php') !== 'd40f1144839238e983ec043dc5210a772df7fdbf') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/VtsBrowserDownload.class.php') !== 'c8810a1fff99d4ff9b3796e205c379147c678c5d') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/VtsBrowserDownload.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/VtsBrowserDownload.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/VtsBrowserDownload.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/VtsBrowserDownload.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_60();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/VtsBrowserDownload.class.php') !== 'd40f1144839238e983ec043dc5210a772df7fdbf') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/VtsBrowserDownload.class.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/functions.inc.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/functions.inc.php');
	writefile_66();
	if (!is_file('includes/functions.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/functions.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/functions.inc.php') != '8efabc404d4ab225bb3d50456b2b2f177981a884') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/functions.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/functions.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/functions.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/functions.inc.php') !== '8efabc404d4ab225bb3d50456b2b2f177981a884') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/functions.inc.php') !== '52ce9413890dc9d32a549dfa5ee9ccd46451270c') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/functions.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/functions.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/functions.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/functions.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_66();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/functions.inc.php') !== '8efabc404d4ab225bb3d50456b2b2f177981a884') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/functions.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/oidplus.inc.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/oidplus.inc.php');
	writefile_67();
	if (!is_file('includes/oidplus.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/oidplus.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/oidplus.inc.php') != 'cd73d60f36ba9f2e4d2754c15012de9ceabfeea6') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/oidplus.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/oidplus.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/oidplus.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/oidplus.inc.php') !== 'cd73d60f36ba9f2e4d2754c15012de9ceabfeea6') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/oidplus.inc.php') !== '12a0763180c2e0286c9f40386559d9598813a48b') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/oidplus.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/oidplus.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/oidplus.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/oidplus.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_67();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/oidplus.inc.php') !== 'cd73d60f36ba9f2e4d2754c15012de9ceabfeea6') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/oidplus.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('index.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: index.php');
	writefile_68();
	if (!is_file('index.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): index.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('index.php') != 'f7b22ff22214015265817f3de0291ffa8971740c') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): index.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('index.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of index.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('index.php') !== 'f7b22ff22214015265817f3de0291ffa8971740c') {
		if (@sha1_file('index.php') !== '5f0b619f1e97b0b08f38d4857840ead03ee8b1a2') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: index.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('index.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('index.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('index.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_68();
		if (@sha1_file('index.php') !== 'f7b22ff22214015265817f3de0291ffa8971740c') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): index.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('oidplus.min.js.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: oidplus.min.js.php');
	writefile_69();
	if (!is_file('oidplus.min.js.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): oidplus.min.js.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('oidplus.min.js.php') != '12ae9c8570c142bb166a719ce668be587d63ac36') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): oidplus.min.js.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('oidplus.min.js.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of oidplus.min.js.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('oidplus.min.js.php') !== '12ae9c8570c142bb166a719ce668be587d63ac36') {
		if (@sha1_file('oidplus.min.js.php') !== '6cb8963e25024bb0a162d72d3615bc242589625d') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: oidplus.min.js.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('oidplus.min.js.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('oidplus.min.js.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('oidplus.min.js.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_69();
		if (@sha1_file('oidplus.min.js.php') !== '12ae9c8570c142bb166a719ce668be587d63ac36') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): oidplus.min.js.php');
		}
	}
}

	if (!is_file('oidplus_base.css')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): oidplus_base.css');
	} else if (sha1_file('oidplus_base.css') != '2d9183009a768c6a70cf16ca49d6fb6d93089ab1') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): oidplus_base.css');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('oidplus_base.css', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of oidplus_base.css');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('oidplus_base.css') !== '2d9183009a768c6a70cf16ca49d6fb6d93089ab1') {
		if (@sha1_file('oidplus_base.css') !== '7caa74d20c511f231911734b9d44b678c9ae5601') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: oidplus_base.css');
			$tmp = pathinfo('oidplus_base.css');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('oidplus_base.css')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('oidplus_base.css', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_70();
		if (@sha1_file('oidplus_base.css') !== '2d9183009a768c6a70cf16ca49d6fb6d93089ab1') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): oidplus_base.css');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.class.php');
	writefile_88();
	if (!is_file('plugins/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.class.php') != '3bdefb516058e76511f827c182ab06597ba80b7c') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.class.php') !== '3bdefb516058e76511f827c182ab06597ba80b7c') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.class.php') !== 'ce67b8f258926b437cb4b1e87b5828d5d1123f99') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.class.php');

			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_88();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.class.php') !== '3bdefb516058e76511f827c182ab06597ba80b7c') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.class.php');

if (!is_file('plugins/adminPages/700_colors/script.js')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/adminPages/700_colors/script.js');
	writefile_89();
	if (!is_file('plugins/adminPages/700_colors/script.js')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/adminPages/700_colors/script.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/700_colors/script.js') != '8f2d5a652bdb1746c41497376767da18dd039547') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/adminPages/700_colors/script.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/adminPages/700_colors/script.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/adminPages/700_colors/script.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/700_colors/script.js') !== '8f2d5a652bdb1746c41497376767da18dd039547') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/700_colors/script.js') !== 'bf290a204b6fe6c14212006992960d5099a5853e') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/adminPages/700_colors/script.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/adminPages/700_colors/script.js');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/adminPages/700_colors/script.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/adminPages/700_colors/script.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_89();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/700_colors/script.js') !== '8f2d5a652bdb1746c41497376767da18dd039547') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/adminPages/700_colors/script.js');
		}
	}
}

	writefile_102();

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/database/sqlite3/OIDplusDatabaseConnectionSQLite3.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/database/sqlite3/OIDplusDatabaseConnectionSQLite3.class.php') != 'ddd195892b22fc3cd402de903e423486dd900c06') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/database/sqlite3/OIDplusDatabaseConnectionSQLite3.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/database/sqlite3/OIDplusDatabaseConnectionSQLite3.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/database/sqlite3/OIDplusDatabaseConnectionSQLite3.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/sqlite3/OIDplusDatabaseConnectionSQLite3.class.php') !== 'ddd195892b22fc3cd402de903e423486dd900c06') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/sqlite3/OIDplusDatabaseConnectionSQLite3.class.php') !== '6b3972fd3ce5b572ee4aed72e32c4cf44fac6923') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/database/sqlite3/OIDplusDatabaseConnectionSQLite3.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/database/sqlite3/OIDplusDatabaseConnectionSQLite3.class.php');

			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/database/sqlite3/OIDplusDatabaseConnectionSQLite3.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_102();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/sqlite3/OIDplusDatabaseConnectionSQLite3.class.php') !== 'ddd195892b22fc3cd402de903e423486dd900c06') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/database/sqlite3/OIDplusDatabaseConnectionSQLite3.class.php');

if (!is_file('plugins/database/sqlite3/OIDplusQueryResultSQLite3.class.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/database/sqlite3/OIDplusQueryResultSQLite3.class.php');
	writefile_103();
	if (!is_file('plugins/database/sqlite3/OIDplusQueryResultSQLite3.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/database/sqlite3/OIDplusQueryResultSQLite3.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/database/sqlite3/OIDplusQueryResultSQLite3.class.php') != '2eee3ec433819cd3b1e0edd50d2833a9dd3c34a2') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/database/sqlite3/OIDplusQueryResultSQLite3.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/database/sqlite3/OIDplusQueryResultSQLite3.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/database/sqlite3/OIDplusQueryResultSQLite3.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/sqlite3/OIDplusQueryResultSQLite3.class.php') !== '2eee3ec433819cd3b1e0edd50d2833a9dd3c34a2') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/sqlite3/OIDplusQueryResultSQLite3.class.php') !== '034aefdcb3adc0721fc1763c29220e87c427ccc2') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/database/sqlite3/OIDplusQueryResultSQLite3.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/database/sqlite3/OIDplusQueryResultSQLite3.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/database/sqlite3/OIDplusQueryResultSQLite3.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/database/sqlite3/OIDplusQueryResultSQLite3.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_103();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/sqlite3/OIDplusQueryResultSQLite3.class.php') !== '2eee3ec433819cd3b1e0edd50d2833a9dd3c34a2') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/database/sqlite3/OIDplusQueryResultSQLite3.class.php');
		}
	}
}

	}
} else {

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/objectTypes/ipv4/OIDplusIpv4.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/objectTypes/ipv4/OIDplusIpv4.class.php') != '5537f820d88c2f6a27f8ac904aa963ce1147be12') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/objectTypes/ipv4/OIDplusIpv4.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/objectTypes/ipv4/OIDplusIpv4.class.php', 0644)) {

	}

	if (@sha1_file('plugins/objectTypes/ipv4/OIDplusIpv4.class.php') !== '5537f820d88c2f6a27f8ac904aa963ce1147be12') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/objectTypes/ipv4/OIDplusIpv4.class.php') !== '5b570ca9684853f1f12eb85edb6f523d76196ef4') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/objectTypes/ipv4/OIDplusIpv4.class.php');

				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}

		if (@sha1_file('plugins/objectTypes/ipv4/OIDplusIpv4.class.php') !== '5537f820d88c2f6a27f8ac904aa963ce1147be12') {

			if (!@copy('plugins/publicPages/000_objects/OIDplusPagePublicObjects.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_118();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/000_objects/OIDplusPagePublicObjects.class.php') !== 'c70a32a3d6edd18dc648fec6393b7b716c0c2007') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/000_objects/OIDplusPagePublicObjects.class.php');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/publicPages/090_login/script.js');
	writefile_124();
	if (!is_file('plugins/publicPages/090_login/script.js')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/publicPages/090_login/script.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/090_login/script.js') != '46834bb6f704d33159a3969f34f2961d78703753') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/090_login/script.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/publicPages/090_login/script.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/publicPages/090_login/script.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/090_login/script.js') !== '46834bb6f704d33159a3969f34f2961d78703753') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/090_login/script.js') !== '6685ef622bd98010dee52e83ac42663d97ddaf09') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/publicPages/090_login/script.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/publicPages/090_login/script.js');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/publicPages/090_login/script.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/publicPages/090_login/script.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_124();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/090_login/script.js') !== '46834bb6f704d33159a3969f34f2961d78703753') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/090_login/script.js');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php');
	writefile_135();
	if (!is_file('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php') != 'ecc1f2d0a6a6fbc3bc5f17c5a68b0c2e0daef037') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php') !== 'ecc1f2d0a6a6fbc3bc5f17c5a68b0c2e0daef037') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php') !== 'db3e560a4df687cf796d89ffb5d7125d286bcde2') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_135();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php') !== 'ecc1f2d0a6a6fbc3bc5f17c5a68b0c2e0daef037') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/sqlSlang/sqlite/OIDplusSqlSlangPluginSQLite.class.php');
	writefile_156();
	if (!is_file('plugins/sqlSlang/sqlite/OIDplusSqlSlangPluginSQLite.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/sqlSlang/sqlite/OIDplusSqlSlangPluginSQLite.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/sqlSlang/sqlite/OIDplusSqlSlangPluginSQLite.class.php') != '3184f32bea317d1c8dd80db13b26a0d8983560ef') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/sqlSlang/sqlite/OIDplusSqlSlangPluginSQLite.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/sqlSlang/sqlite/OIDplusSqlSlangPluginSQLite.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/sqlSlang/sqlite/OIDplusSqlSlangPluginSQLite.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/sqlSlang/sqlite/OIDplusSqlSlangPluginSQLite.class.php') !== '3184f32bea317d1c8dd80db13b26a0d8983560ef') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/sqlSlang/sqlite/OIDplusSqlSlangPluginSQLite.class.php') !== 'b7fd60e63c87dd9629449c3275a4ed769c51a8d2') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/sqlSlang/sqlite/OIDplusSqlSlangPluginSQLite.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/sqlSlang/sqlite/OIDplusSqlSlangPluginSQLite.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/sqlSlang/sqlite/OIDplusSqlSlangPluginSQLite.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/sqlSlang/sqlite/OIDplusSqlSlangPluginSQLite.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_156();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/sqlSlang/sqlite/OIDplusSqlSlangPluginSQLite.class.php') !== '3184f32bea317d1c8dd80db13b26a0d8983560ef') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/sqlSlang/sqlite/OIDplusSqlSlangPluginSQLite.class.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html');
	writefile_157();
	if (!is_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html');
	} else if (sha1_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html') != '8a5fa390ef4d231620535ac657eca8ec5e1ad41e') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html') !== '8a5fa390ef4d231620535ac657eca8ec5e1ad41e') {
		if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html') !== '716bb51fbe9e2f63c816048680946d4cbe21c0fc') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html');
			$tmp = pathinfo('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_157();
		if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html') !== '8a5fa390ef4d231620535ac657eca8ec5e1ad41e') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('update/index.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: update/index.php');
	writefile_163();
	if (!is_file('update/index.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): update/index.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('update/index.php') != '4f0276d3255f9ccdd9c7c682f593cf0c777251da') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): update/index.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('update/index.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of update/index.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('update/index.php') !== '4f0276d3255f9ccdd9c7c682f593cf0c777251da') {
		if (@sha1_file('update/index.php') !== '1003f71b8710142ec3c24aa880d6cfdd9039f26d') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: update/index.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('update/index.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('update/index.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('update/index.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_163();
		if (@sha1_file('update/index.php') !== '4f0276d3255f9ccdd9c7c682f593cf0c777251da') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): update/index.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('userdata/info.txt')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: userdata/info.txt');
	writefile_164();
	if (!is_file('userdata/info.txt')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): userdata/info.txt');
	} else if (sha1_file('userdata/info.txt') != '14c2381fb12b7b7d58ce1ff3aa93c060c72aa393') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): userdata/info.txt');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('userdata/info.txt', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of userdata/info.txt');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('userdata/info.txt') !== '14c2381fb12b7b7d58ce1ff3aa93c060c72aa393') {
		if (@sha1_file('userdata/info.txt') !== '357a92b044b1e1ca51f8b26a6bfbc6d29f5e39d5') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: userdata/info.txt');
			$tmp = pathinfo('userdata/info.txt');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('userdata/info.txt')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('userdata/info.txt', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_164();
		if (@sha1_file('userdata/info.txt') !== '14c2381fb12b7b7d58ce1ff3aa93c060c72aa393') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): userdata/info.txt');
		}
	}
}
